items.title: How Nepal’s Government Went Up in Smoke
items.description: Arson attacks during protests in Nepal destroyed buildings, court files and even records of international agreements and state investments.

items.title: Climate Change’s Toll in Europe This Summer: Thousands of Extra Deaths
